
            
                1 Have you ever worked for a charity?How long did you work there?Was it a well run charity?Did you enjoy this work?
            
                2 Do you give money to registered charities? (e.g. Red Cross, World Wildlife Fund, Green Peace)Can you name some other registered charities?
            
                3 Do you think having large charity organizations is a good idea? Why or why not?What are some of the good points?What are some of the bad points?
            
                4 Do you think that locally run charity organizations are more effective?
            
                5 Are there any charities in (your town/city)?How about in (your country)?What are they?
